show.description: A billionaire hiding his true identity works as a food delivery boy, determined to reclaim his fortune. But as greedy relatives conspire to stop him, his journey becomes a thrilling battle of wits and will. A powerful tale of revenge, resilience, and the triumph of honesty over greed.
